# Git Workflow — Agricart ERP

## Branches

- **`main`** — deployment-safe; Hostinger production always pulls from `main`
- **`develop`** — all new work is committed here first
- Never push directly to `main` without explicit user confirmation

## Before Any Push

1. Run `git status`
2. Show current branch
3. Explain exactly what commits/files will be pushed
4. Ask for user approval — do not push until approved

## Before Merging develop → main

1. Review all changes (`git diff main...develop`, commit log)
2. Check for errors (tests, lint, broken routes if applicable)
3. Confirm deployment readiness with the user
4. Ask for explicit merge approval — never merge automatically

## Prohibited Without Confirmation

- `git push` (any branch)
- `git merge`
- Deployment actions (Hostinger pull, artisan on production, etc.)

## Workflow

```
feature/fix work → commit on develop → review → merge to main (approved) → deploy from main
```

## Milestone

`main` at commit `3828543` ("Phase 1 UI Foundation Complete") is the stable UI Foundation baseline.
